# MFFD raw industrial data drop from ZLP Augsburg. NEVER enters the repo —
# this is multi-GB DLR-internal manufacturing data (AFP, NDT, welding, LBR),
# not seed-able synthetic content. `examples/mffd-showcase/seed.py` already
# generates a synthetic surrogate that IS committed.
#
# Pattern covers:
#   raw-data/      — the directory itself
#   raw-data/*     — anything directly inside
#   raw-data/**    — anything at any nesting depth
# Force-add overrides are intentionally NOT provided — if a file from here
# ever needs to be tracked it should be moved to a separate, sanitised
# location with explicit IP review.
raw-data/
raw-data/*
raw-data/**

# Importer per-session artefacts — generated by mffd-import-v15.py + runner.sh.
# Documented in scripts/README.md; never committed (logs grow to many MB,
# state files carry session-specific JWT footprints, staged self-update files
# are temporary by definition).
scripts/mffd-import-*.log
scripts/.mffd-import.lock
scripts/mffd-import-*.state.json
scripts/mffd-import-v15.v*.new
scripts/mffd-import-v15.py.bak.*
